# Store API - Test Requests

### Get all products
GET http://localhost:3000/products

###

### Get single product by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/products/REPLACE_WITH_REAL_ID

###

### Create a new product
POST http://localhost:3000/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Wireless Headphones",
  "description": "High quality noise-cancelling wireless headphones",
  "price": 99.99,
  "category": "Electronics",
  "brand": "Sony",
  "stock": 50,
  "rating": 4.5
}

###

### Update a product
PUT http://localhost:3000/products/REPLACE_WITH_REAL_ID
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Wireless Headphones Pro",
  "description": "Updated noise-cancelling wireless headphones",
  "price": 129.99,
  "category": "Electronics",
  "brand": "Sony",
  "stock": 30,
  "rating": 4.8
}

###

### Delete a product
DELETE http://localhost:3000/products/REPLACE_WITH_REAL_ID

###

### Get all categories
GET http://localhost:3000/categories

###

### Get single category by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/categories/REPLACE_WITH_REAL_ID

###

### Create a new category
POST http://localhost:3000/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Electronics",
  "description": "Electronic devices and accessories"
}

###

### Update a category
PUT http://localhost:3000/categories/REPLACE_WITH_REAL_ID
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Electronics & Gadgets",
  "description": "Electronic devices, gadgets and accessories"
}

###

### Delete a category
DELETE http://localhost:3000/categories/REPLACE_WITH_REAL_ID
